<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Status Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .header.pending { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107 0%, #fd7e14 100%); }
        .header.reviewing { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #17a2b8 0%, #007bff 100%); }
        .header.shortlisted { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); }
        .header.interviewed { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6f42c1 0%, #e83e8c 100%); }
        .header.offered { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); }
        .header.hired { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); }
        .header.rejected { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%); }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .status-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .status-card.pending { border-left-color: #ffc107; }
        .status-card.reviewing { border-left-color: #17a2b8; }
        .status-card.shortlisted { border-left-color: #28a745; }
        .status-card.interviewed { border-left-color: #6f42c1; }
        .status-card.offered { border-left-color: #28a745; }
        .status-card.hired { border-left-color: #28a745; }
        .status-card.rejected { border-left-color: #dc3545; }
        
        .job-info {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .job-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            background: #e7f3ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }
        .job-details h3 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #212529;
        }
        .job-details p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .timeline {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .timeline-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .timeline-icon.completed {
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
        }
        .timeline-icon.current {
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
        }
        .timeline-icon.pending {
            background: #e9ecef;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border: 2px solid #b3d7ff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .steps-list li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 30px;
        }
        .steps-list li:before {
            content: "‚Üí";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header {{status}}">
            <h1>Application Status Update</h1>
            <p>{{statusMessage}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
            
            <p>We have an update regarding your job application:</p>
            
            <div class="job-info">
                <div class="job-icon">üíº</div>
                <div class="job-details">
                    <h3>{{jobTitle}}</h3>
                    <p><strong>{{companyName}}</strong></p>
                    <p>Application Status: <strong>{{capitalize status}}</strong></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="status-card {{status}}">
                {{#ifEquals status "pending"}}
                <h4>‚è≥ Application Under Review</h4>
                <p>Your application has been received and is currently being reviewed by the hiring team. We'll keep you updated as the process progresses.</p>
                {{/ifEquals}}
                
                {{#ifEquals status "reviewing"}}
                <h4>üëÄ Application Being Reviewed</h4>
                <p>Great news! Your application has caught the attention of the hiring team and is currently under detailed review.</p>
                {{/ifEquals}}
                
                {{#ifEquals status "shortlisted"}}
                <h4>üåü Congratulations! You've Been Shortlisted</h4>
                <p>Excellent news! You've been selected as one of the top candidates for this position. The hiring team will be in touch soon to discuss next steps.</p>
                {{/ifEquals}}
                
                {{#ifEquals status "interviewed"}}
                <h4>üé§ Interview Completed</h4>
                <p>Thank you for taking the time to interview with us. The hiring team is now reviewing all candidates and will make a decision soon.</p>
                {{/ifEquals}}
                
                {{#ifEquals status "offered"}}
                <h4>üéâ Congratulations! Job Offer Extended</h4>
                <p>We're thrilled to extend you an offer for this position! Please review the offer details and respond by the specified deadline.</p>
                {{/ifEquals}}
                
                {{#ifEquals status "hired"}}
                <h4>üéä Welcome to the Team!</h4>
                <p>Congratulations! We're excited to welcome you to the team. You'll receive onboarding information shortly.</p>
                {{/ifEquals}}
                
                {{#ifEquals status "rejected"}}
                <h4>Thank You for Your Interest</h4>
                <p>While we've decided to move forward with other candidates for this particular role, we were impressed by your qualifications and encourage you to apply for future opportunities.</p>
                {{/ifEquals}}
            </div>
            
            {{#if nextSteps}}
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>üìã Next Steps</h3>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    {{#each nextSteps}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="timeline">
                <h3>üìÖ Application Timeline</h3>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon completed">‚úì</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Application Submitted</strong>
                        <p>Your application was successfully submitted</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon {{#ifEquals status 'pending'}}current{{else}}completed{{/ifEquals}}">üëÄ</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Under Review</strong>
                        <p>Application is being reviewed by hiring team</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                {{#if (or (ifEquals status "shortlisted") (ifEquals status "interviewed") (ifEquals status "offered") (ifEquals status "hired"))}}
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon {{#ifEquals status 'shortlisted'}}current{{else}}completed{{/ifEquals}}">‚≠ê</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Shortlisted</strong>
                        <p>Selected as a top candidate</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                {{#if (or (ifEquals status "interviewed") (ifEquals status "offered") (ifEquals status "hired"))}}
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon {{#ifEquals status 'interviewed'}}current{{else}}completed{{/ifEquals}}">üé§</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Interview</strong>
                        <p>Interview process completed</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                {{#if (or (ifEquals status "offered") (ifEquals status "hired"))}}
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon {{#ifEquals status 'offered'}}current{{else}}completed{{/ifEquals}}">üéâ</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>{{#ifEquals status "hired"}}Hired{{else}}Offer Extended{{/ifEquals}}</strong>
                        <p>{{#ifEquals status "hired"}}Welcome to the team!{{else}}Job offer has been extended{{/ifEquals}}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{applicationUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Application Details</a>
                {{#ifEquals status "offered"}}
                <a href="{{applicationUrl}}/offer" class="cta-button">Review Offer</a>
                {{/ifEquals}}
            </div>
            
            {{#ifEquals status "rejected"}}
            <div style="background: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; color: #721c24;">
                <h4>üöÄ Keep Moving Forward</h4>
                <p>Don't let this discourage you! Here are some ways to improve your chances:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Update your resume with our AI suggestions</li>
                    <li>Apply to similar positions</li>
                    <li>Enhance your skills based on market trends</li>
                    <li>Network with professionals in your field</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/ifEquals}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Resume Refresh Platform</strong></p>
            <p>Supporting your career journey every step of the way</p>
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd;">
                This is an automated update about your job application.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
